Prepare pasta according to package directions. Drain, reserving 1/2 cup cooking water. While pasta is cooking, prepare zucchini mixture. Heat oil in large skillet over medium-high heat. Add zucchini and garlic; cook, stirring frequently, for 3 to 4 minutes or until zucchini starts to turn golden. Season with salt and pepper. Add pasta, reserved cooking water and mozzarella cheese to skillet; toss to coat. Serve garnished with grated lemon peel and sliced almonds.